This charatcer is the druid in the druid tree in the city core. He tries to get the player to go to a zoo in another district and free the animals within.


The animals inthe zoo can be talked to once freed. They can be told to escape, or to kill the guards, then escape, or kill innocents and escape.
If the player cannot talk to the animals, he can use a scented fetish to make the animals follow him. 

To escape, the animals are supposed to go to the tree outside the zoo. The player is supposed to use a "transport via plants" scroll on the tree. If they are following him, they stop when they get near the tree that the plant transport spell was used on. 

If the player does not use the scroll on the tree, the animals follow him until he gets near the druid tree in the city core. Then they enter and destroy themselves.
